port/student-financial-planning/" class="fusion-bar-highlight" role="menuitem"><span>Student Financial Planning</span></a></li><li  id="menu-item-6581"  class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-6581" ><a  href="https://medicine.uic.edu/education/md-student-services-and-support/student-honors-and-awards/" class="fusion-bar-highlight" role="menuitem"><span>Student Honors and Awards</span></a></li></ul></li><li  id="menu-item-592"  class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-592 fusion-dropdown-submenu" ><a  href="https://medicine.uic.edu/education/md-student-life/" class="fusion-bar-highlight" role="menuitem"><span>MD Student Life</span></a></li><li  id="menu-item-4767"  class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-has-children menu-item-4767 fusion-dropdown-submenu" ><a  href="https://medicine.uic.edu/education/educational-environment/" class="fusion-bar-highlight" role="menuitem"><span>Educational Environment</span></a><ul role="menu" class="sub-menu"><li  id="menu-item-5299"  class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-5299" ><a  href="https://medicine.uic.edu/education/educational-environment/director-of-medical-student-learning-environment-3/" class="fusion-bar-highlight" role="menuitem"><span>Director of Medical Student Learning Environment</span></a></li><li  id="menu-item-4768"  class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-4768" ><a  href="https://medicine.uic.edu/education/educational-environment/reporting/" class="fusion-bar-highlight" role="menuitem"><span>Reporting Mistreatment or Concerns</span></a></li><li  id="menu-item-5300"  class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-has-children menu-item-5300" ><a  href="https://medicine.uic.edu/education/educational-environment/college-policy-guidelines/" class="fusion-bar-highlight" role="menuitem"><span>College Policy &#038; Guideline